data.description: OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY, NOV 11TH, 11-1! This Reynoldsburg home sits on a huge corner lot and is centrally located between Broad & Main. Just off of the kitchen, you will find a 4 season room, eat-in kitchen, family room & dining room. The upstairs features a recently updated master en-suite with new flooring, a full bathroom and a walk-in closet.  In addition, the home boasts a tankless water heater (2021), laundry areas on both the 1st floor & lower level, a whole house Kohler Generator, new furnace (2021), & new air conditioner (2021).  Need extra parking?  Not only do you get an enclosed garage, but you also get a carport.  Freshly painted throughout.  May qualify for $15,000 grant & no closing costs!
